# This should look like:
# 
# +         +         +         +         +         +
# +-------------------+---------+-------------------+ +
# |        CPU        |   MEM   |       PROCS       |
# +---------+---------+---------+                   | +
# |  TEMPS  |       DISK        |                   |
# |         |                   |                   | +
# |         |                   |                   |
# |         +-------------------+                   | +
# |         |       POWER       |                   |
# +---------+-------------------+                   | +
# |            NET              |                   |
# +-----------------------------+-------------------+ +
#

# Not all of the weights are necessary (e.g., power, net) nor
# the spacing, but it makes the layout easier to visualize.

cpu/2           mem/1     5:procs/2
3:temp/1        2:disk/2
                power/2
net/3

